article_title: TODAY'S QUESTION: Will federal courts be able to establish a compromise on the Obamacare contraceptive mandate?
article_text:
Supreme Court Sends "Contraceptive Mandate" Back To Lower Courts

Mark Wilson / Getty Images

The early morning sun rises behind the U.S. Supreme Court building Monday in Washington, D.C., where the high court sent the Affordable Care Act's contraceptive mandate case back down to lower courts for a compromise.
